### GET conversations by userId
GET http://localhost:4000/api/conversations/b07e2e98-4a0f-4a7e-b376-8f72c87d3a4b

### GET mesages from conversation
GET http://localhost:4000/api/conversations/98b1ea20-bb91-48c2-8347-3fe67cfc12eb/messages

### POST create a new conversation
POST http://localhost:4000/api/conversations
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "participantIds": ["b07e2e98-4a0f-4a7e-b376-8f72c87d3a4b", "a9d3c48f-1fdb-466e-b9c3-3f62dccb4856"]
}

### POST Send message to conversation
POST http://localhost:4000/api/conversations/98b1ea20-bb91-48c2-8347-3fe67cfc12eb/messages
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "senderId": "a9d3c48f-1fdb-466e-b9c3-3f62dccb4856",
  "content": "Now multiline is working\nYou see? It works!!!"
}

